{"about_the_game":"<i>There they stood all steeped in shame, another victim claimed in my name. </i><br><br><strong>The Murder Hotel</strong> is an interactive Murder Mystery Adventure with a huge twist: A scissors wielding demon is the murderer and you have to blame one of the human guests, forging a plausible theory how they could have done it.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1969170/extras/GAST2.png?t=1736816179\" /> <br><i>Feel free to call me Gastfenger. I'm the demonic hotelier, at your service.<br><br>Oh, you want to leave already? How amusing.<br>Nobody leaves this place unless I allow it.<br><br>How about you solve 4 murder cases. Easy, you say?<br>There's a twist to them. It is I who murders my own guests.<br>And it's your task to investigate and successfully blame <strong>one of the other guests</strong> as the culprit.<br><br>Defeat your rival and convince the Demon Council to win a case.<br>Lose just once, and you'll stay here, forever!<br><br>Dare challenge me?</i><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">About the game</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1969170/extras/WILDMIX.png?t=1736816179\" /><li>A demon may be the perpetrator but you can only explain each murder by human methods. Are you up to the challenge?<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1969170/extras/SECRETS.png?t=1736816179\" /><br></li><li>Find out why the murders are happening and how to put an end to them.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1969170/extras/CHARACTERS.png?t=1736816179\" /><br></li><li>Featuring 14 human guests and a handful of demons, all with their own backstories and dark secrets.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1969170/extras/CRIME.png?t=1736816179\" /><br></li><li>Find clues in the form of paper words and form your own sentences to interrogate suspects<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1969170/extras/DEMON.png?t=1736816179\" /><br></li><li>There's multiple ways and theories to win a trial. Can you find them all?</li></ul><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1969170/extras/Characters_-_Female.png?t=1736816179\" /><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1969170/extras/Characters_-_Male.png?t=1736816179\" />","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1969170/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1736816179","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1969170/page_bg_generated.jpg?t=1736816179","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1969170/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1736816179","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1969170/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1736816179","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Full controller support","id":28}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[],"notes":null},"controller_support":"full","demos":[{"appid":2484850,"description":""}],"detailed_description":"<i>There they stood all steeped in shame, another victim claimed in my name. </i><br><br><strong>The Murder Hotel</strong> is an interactive Murder Mystery Adventure with a huge twist: A scissors wielding demon is the murderer and you have to blame one of the human guests, forging a plausible theory how they could have done it.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1969170/extras/GAST2.png?t=1736816179\" /> <br><i>Feel free to call me Gastfenger. I'm the demonic hotelier, at your service.<br><br>Oh, you w